OL,3,CHealth body writes to parents after
OL,4,CHepatitis A outbreak in Welsh town
OL,6,FA small number of Hepatitis A cases of
OL,7,Fthe same strain have been identified
OL,8,Fin three separate households in Barry.
OL,10,FPHW, working with Cardiff and Vale
OL,11,FHealth Board, said the infection may
OL,12,Fbe spreading locally.
OL,14,FA team of health experts has been
OL,15,Fbrought together to understand how the
OL,16,Finfection is spreading.
OL,18,FThose who have been unwell are
OL,19,Freceiving appropriate care and are
OL,20,Frecovering well, the health body said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
