OL,3,CHealth body writes to parents after
OL,4,CHepatitis A outbreak in Welsh town
OL,6,FVaccination has been offered to people
OL,7,Fwho have been in close contact with
OL,8,Fthose infected as a precaution and PHW
OL,9,Fhas contacted everyone identified as
OL,10,Fneeding a vaccine.
OL,12,FSusan Mably, Consultant in Health
OL,13,FProtection for PHW said the body is
OL,14,Fwriting to parents who have children
OL,15,Fin primary schools in Barry to ask
OL,16,Fthem to be vigilant with their
OL,17,Fchildren's handwashing to prevent
OL,18,Ffurther spread of infection.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
