OL,3,CHealth body writes to parents after
OL,4,CHepatitis A outbreak in Welsh town
OL,6,F"The best way to prevent the spread of
OL,7,FHepatitis A is to wash hands
OL,8,Fthoroughly with soap and water. This
OL,9,Fis important after using the toilet,
OL,10,Fchanging nappies and before preparing
OL,11,For eating food," she said.
OL,13,F"Some young children who are infected
OL,14,Fmay not show any symptoms but can
OL,15,Fspread the infection to others who can
OL,16,Fthen become unwell.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
