OL,3,CHealth body writes to parents after
OL,4,CHepatitis A outbreak in Welsh town
OL,6,F"Parents and carers should help and
OL,7,Fremind young children to wash their
OL,8,Fhands properly. If you or your child
OL,9,Ffeels unwell and have symptoms such as
OL,10,Fa fever, feeling very tired, a loss of
OL,11,Fappetite, feeling sick or being sick
OL,12,For have yellow skin or eyes you should
OL,13,Fcontact your GP or NHS 111 Wales."
